title: Here's Channing Tatum Tap-Dancing in a Sailor Suit, Because You Deserve It
text:
​Channing Tatum stars in the upcoming Coen brothers movie ​Hail, Caesar! ​, and now there's a new trailer in which you can see him tap dancing. In a sailor suit. On a table. Congratulations, it's your birthday! Channing's sailor dance starts around the 1:12 mark, but you should watch the rest of the trailer because (1) this movie looks ridiculous and amazing and (2) Scarlett Johansson also appears as a mermaid. Maybe if they ever make a third ​Magic Mike ​, Channing will find a way to recycle this costume and these moves. Something tells me the Kings of Tampa could do a lot with "In the Navy."
